Maybe he wants you to just
be listening constantly

00:09:50.080 --> 00:09:54.390
and on a dime have to be able
to switch, devise some structure

00:09:54.390 --> 00:09:55.890
within the piece by yourself.

00:09:55.890 --> 00:09:58.670 position:56%
And definitely interpret,
interpret, interpret the whole time.

00:09:58.670 --> 00:09:59.970
So.

