cycling through these three notes.

00:12:05.120 --> 00:12:07.250
And I thought that is a
fascinating place to start.

00:12:07.250 --> 00:12:11.450
So I kind of put the flute
as the description of kind

00:12:11.450 --> 00:12:12.860
of what is going on around there.

00:12:12.860 --> 00:12:16.160
And then I had the cello and
base clarinet representing kind

00:12:16.160 --> 00:12:18.950
of the inner turmoil of the scene.

00:12:18.950 --> 00:12:23.880
So one is expressing the outward
serenity or absurdity and the.

00:12:23.880 --> 00:12:29.290
And then the lower instruments
