00:12:29.290 --> 00:12:31.330
And these two kind of coincide.

00:12:31.330 --> 00:12:34.770
They first start off very
separately and they come together.

00:12:34.770 --> 00:12:36.230
&gt;&gt; David Plylar: You know one
