00:23:20.930 --> 00:23:23.760
And it is something that
kind of creates this.

00:23:23.760 --> 00:23:26.920
These moments of interaction
that you can kind of anticipate.

00:23:26.920 --> 00:23:28.220
But you are not quite
sure how he is going

00:23:28.220 --> 00:23:31.180
to handle each interaction
