&gt;&gt; Taka Kigawa: [Inaudible] and
I am also revisiting [inaudible]

00:36:57.240 --> 00:36:58.540
and also [inaudible].

00:36:58.540 --> 00:37:04.910
So. This whole thing
is jabbling [laughter].

00:37:04.910 --> 00:37:06.210
&gt;&gt; David Plylar: Wow.

00:37:06.210 --> 00:37:10.150
Why don't we take a moment now just
to, if anybody has any questions

00:37:10.150 --> 00:37:14.980
for these guys before we let them
